Ask HN: Any good BI tools for DevOps/Engineers?
text:
We use a lot of tools and systems: Azure, AWS, Azure DevOps, Cloudflare, GitHub, Jira.

Are there any good BI tools, specifically for this kind of data for reporting SLOs, incidents, MTTR, cost etc.?

There’s plenty (!) of more generic tools like Tableau or Qlik, but they’re don’t feel well suited to the data in an engineering or product context.

Any cool projects or tools out there?

Thank you!
